title: Ep. 11 - Manpon
description:
On today's episode, the guys discuss a mysterious object that washed up in South Carolina that is definitely an alien object, a woman bringing a squirrel on a flight as a support animal, and a man having an interesting run-in in a church in North Dakota. Todd also wants to know what female product the guys would like to endorse, they answer some listener questions, and send you into the weekend with some more Friday Bangerz. Come and have a good time with us.

This episode features @toddmccomas, @PatMcAfeeShow, @Digz, @nickmaraldo, @tyschmit, @BostonConnr, @VivalaZito, and @baileymccomas
